  "aboutFeaturesBody": "Photo-based species and disease analysis (mostly on-device)\nScan history with species grouping and photos\nHealth progress: 14/30-day disease trend charts\nMy plants: pot-level records linked to scans\nFollow-up notifications when health score is low\nPDF report download and share\nCare guide, daily tips, and multi-plant region selection",
